de.fuberlin.panda.metadata.result.fusion.clustering

Class ClusteringResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fuberlin.panda.metadata.result.fusion.clustering.ClusteringResult

  • public class ClusteringResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a simple data class which holds the clustering result. There are three different lists which represent the result. The noTimestamps respectively outliers list consist of the metadata indices of the objects which don't have a timestamp respectively are outliers. The clusters list holds lists of metadata indices for every detected cluster.

    25.02.2014
